dct_title_s: Regnum Moreae accuratissime divisum in Provincias Saccaniam, Tzaconiam, Caliscopium et Ducatum Clarensae, una cum Insulis Cephalonia, Zacyntho, Cythera, Aegina et Sidra
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Prime meridian: Ferro. Bar scales given in "milliaria Italica" and "milliaria Germanica." Appeared in Valk and Schenk's Atlantis sylloge compendiosa, ca. 1702.
dct_publisher_sm: [Amsterdam] : Sumptibus Gerardi et Leonardi Valk, cum privil., [ca. 1702?]
